00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:46,359
2571
188...

292
00:20:47,799 --> 00:20:49,119
I see he signed up too.

293
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:55,359
Are you sure you want to confess?

294
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:58,480
Traveling with another class,

295
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:00,000
what a great opportunity!

296
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:03,200
Whether he's studying abroad or not,

297
00:21:03,519 --> 00:21:04,640
whether he has someone he likes or not,

298
00:21:05,559 --> 00:21:06,559
as long as he's single,

299
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:08,079
I, at eighteen,

300
00:21:08,079 --> 00:21:09,240
have the right to confess.

301
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:10,920
I've thought it through.

302
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,480
No matter the outcome,

303
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:14,839
I want to give my youth

304
00:21:15,359 --> 00:21:16,079
a proper closure.

305
00:21:29,519 --> 00:21:31,640
Ruan Yu, here.

306
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:42,359
Stop it.
Stop looking.

307
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:43,680
He hasn't come yet.

308
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:45,200
Not yet?

309
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:47,279
What's the gift?

310
00:22:07,039 --> 00:22:08,160
Why so many stars?

311
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,640
It represents the 1,013 days

312
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:10,640
of our high school life.

313
00:22:11,039 --> 00:22:11,920
Not a single one can be missing.

314
00:22:14,119 --> 00:22:15,039
It took her over a week

315
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:16,799
to fold over a thousand paper stars.

316
00:22:17,279 --> 00:22:19,480
Love is truly powerful.

317
00:22:21,519 --> 00:22:22,880
Look, is it okay?

318
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:26,240
Perfect.

319
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:29,279
Why hasn't he come yet?

320
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:30,079
He should be here soon.
Guys,

321
00:22:31,279 --> 00:22:32,880
we're all here now.

322
00:22:32,880 --> 00:22:33,720
Get ready to board the bus.

323
00:22:34,480 --> 00:22:36,200
Monitor, everyone's here.

324
00:22:37,319 --> 00:22:39,319
Monitor, what about Xu Huaisong?

325
00:22:39,799 --> 00:22:40,599
Xu Huaisong?

326
00:22:40,680 --> 00:22:42,160
The one from Class 10.

327
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:45,359
Xu Huaisong isn't coming?

328
00:22:46,279 --> 00:22:47,720
He's probably not interested

329
00:22:47,720 --> 00:22:48,480
in group activities.

330
00:22:48,759 --> 00:22:50,039
Zhou Jun, get on the bus.

331
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:55,240
You two, hurry up.

332
00:22:55,240 --> 00:22:56,440
There are still seats in the front.

333
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:57,400
Alright, hurry up.

334
00:22:57,920 --> 00:22:58,599
So,

335
00:22:59,319 --> 00:23:00,759
he has no attachment

336
00:23:01,279 --> 00:23:02,599
to anyone here?

337
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:04,279
Should we get on the bus first?

338
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:38,880
Xu Huaisong isn't coming?

339
00:23:39,559 --> 00:23:41,000
He probably doesn't like

340
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:41,720
group activities.

341
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:44,319
The summer graduation trip

342
00:23:44,559 --> 00:23:45,119
of Class 9 and 10, Grade 12,

343
00:23:45,119 --> 00:23:46,599
Suzhou No.1 High School,

344
00:23:46,599 --> 00:23:48,720
Class of 2014, is about to begin.

345
00:23:49,279 --> 00:23:50,519
I hope we can

346
00:23:50,519 --> 00:23:52,559
create beautiful memories

347
00:23:52,559 --> 00:23:54,079
in the last group activity.

348
00:23:54,279 --> 00:23:56,279
Happy graduation.

349
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,839
Okay, fasten your seat belts.

350
00:24:00,839 --> 00:24:01,680
We're about to set off.

351
00:24:21,039 --> 00:24:22,000
In that trip,

352
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:24,000
the heroine

353
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:26,279
prepared a confession.

354
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:28,920
But she didn't wait

355
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:29,880
for the hero.

356
00:24:32,519 --> 00:24:34,599
So the heroine's

357
00:24:34,599 --> 00:24:36,119
confession was doomed

358
00:24:36,680 --> 00:24:37,640
not to be heard

359
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:39,759
from the beginning.

360
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:42,240
The gift she prepared

361
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:44,319
was doomed

362
00:24:44,720 --> 00:24:46,119
not to be given.

363
00:24:50,079 --> 00:24:51,400
Does it sound a little cruel?

364
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:00,799
But for the heroine,

365
00:25:01,559 --> 00:25:03,000
the absence of the hero

366
00:25:03,799 --> 00:25:04,799
actually gives her

367
00:25:04,799 --> 00:25:06,000
an answer.

368
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:09,240
It should be a happy ending.

369
00:25:14,839 --> 00:25:15,519
Why?

370
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:17,440
In this world,

371
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:19,680
the hardest thing to heal

372
00:25:20,319 --> 00:25:21,559
is never a broken heart,

373
00:25:22,559 --> 00:25:23,480
but unrequited love.

374
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:25,759
Because in unrequited love,

375
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:27,960
who have never been rejected

376
00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:29,799
will always have the right

377
00:25:30,279 --> 00:25:31,640
to fantasize about the ending,

378
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:36,559
so they will always tie themselves up in knots.

379
00:25:37,319 --> 00:25:38,960
But once they muster up all their courage

380
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:39,799
to try,

381
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,200
they will be completely crushed.

382
00:25:42,759 --> 00:25:46,240
Then the secret love will turn into

383
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:47,799
a curable heartbreak.

384
00:25:48,839 --> 00:25:49,640
The world is big,

385
00:25:50,519 --> 00:25:51,599
and the years are long,

386
00:25:53,039 --> 00:25:56,440
the heroine will let go of the hero.

387
00:26:10,039 --> 00:26:10,680
Lawyer Xu,

388
00:26:11,079 --> 00:26:11,920
you seem to be speeding.

389
00:26:19,440 --> 00:26:20,160
Readers

390
00:26:20,720 --> 00:26:22,119
won't accept this ending.

391
00:26:23,640 --> 00:26:24,440
Maybe.

392
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:30,000
But the endings of some stories

393
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:32,559
are already predestined.

394
00:26:33,960 --> 00:26:34,839
Creators

395
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:38,359
may not be able to change much.

396
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:10,160
Mom,

397
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:13,319
I'm fine. I didn't get wet.

398
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:14,680
I'm already home now.

399
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:17,880
I didn't take the high-speed train.

400
00:27:18,200 --> 00:27:21,160
I met a friend on the way.

401
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:23,400
Okay.

402
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:25,880
Then you and dad should get some rest early.

403
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:27,759
Good night.

404
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:35,640
Hasn't he left yet?

405
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:09,480
Love only lasts forever in regrets.

406
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:16,079
Perhaps many years later,

407
00:28:16,720 --> 00:28:17,920
she will meet him again.

408
00:28:18,480 --> 00:28:19,519
But by the time they meet,

409
00:28:20,559 --> 00:28:22,079
the heart might have already been worn away

410
00:28:22,079 --> 00:28:23,680
by the worries of life and time.

411
00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:26,599
Love is eternal in regret.

412
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:47,720
Yeah.

413
00:28:48,119 --> 00:28:49,279
In the world literature,

414
00:28:49,759 --> 00:28:51,039
tragedies

415
00:28:51,039 --> 00:28:52,240
are more unforgettable.

416
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:54,799
Why should we change the ending?

417
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,240
The world is so big,

418
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:17,440
and time is so long.

419
00:29:18,799 --> 00:29:22,200
The heroine will let the hero go.

420
00:30:10,160 --> 00:30:11,319
Glutinous rice is hard to digest,

421
00:30:11,640 --> 00:30:13,400
so I didn't put it in.

422
00:30:14,559 --> 00:30:16,240
It may taste a little bit bad.

423
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:19,680
Just make do with it.

424
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:25,799
It's authentic.

425
00:31:02,880 --> 00:31:03,480
Lawyer Xu,

426
00:31:04,160 --> 00:31:05,279
I switched to Suzhou's

427
00:31:05,279 --> 00:31:06,079
pork fat rice cake.

428
00:31:06,319 --> 00:31:07,240
You probably don't

429
00:31:07,240 --> 00:31:08,359
get to eat this abroad, right?

430
00:31:09,799 --> 00:31:10,279
Thank you.

431
00:31:27,359 --> 00:31:27,839
[Brother,]
[have you arrived?]

432
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:29,799
[Remember to hold an umbrella]

433
00:31:29,799 --> 00:31:31,279
[for Sister Ruan Yu when you get off.]

434
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:32,079
Rainy days

435
00:31:32,079 --> 00:31:33,920
are perfect for getting closer.

436
00:31:34,039 --> 00:31:35,200
Make sure to take advantage of it.

437
00:31:38,519 --> 00:31:39,039
What if

438
00:31:39,039 --> 00:31:40,480
there's no chance to hold an umbrella?

439
00:32:01,559 --> 00:32:02,319
Don't worry,

440
00:32:02,839 --> 00:32:04,400
I won't give up.

441
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:06,200
Just give me some time

442
00:32:06,839 --> 00:32:07,920
to plan.

443
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:10,359
The lawsuit

444
00:32:10,599 --> 00:32:11,799
is almost over.

445
00:32:12,319 --> 00:32:13,680
And what about you and Xu Huaisong?

446
00:32:14,039 --> 00:32:15,200
come to an end too?

447
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:16,599
Of course.

448
00:32:17,839 --> 00:32:19,079
After the case is over,

449
00:32:19,799 --> 00:32:21,559
he should go back to the US.

450
00:32:23,319 --> 00:32:25,119
That sounds like a good thing.

451
00:32:25,359 --> 00:32:27,119
You won't have to worry about

452
00:32:27,119 --> 00:32:29,000
being exposed or embarrassed anymore.

453
00:32:31,279 --> 00:32:32,680
What's with the sigh?

454
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:35,759
Do you kind of miss him?

455
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:38,119
Did I just sigh?

456
00:32:40,279 --> 00:32:41,079
Alright.

457
00:32:42,519 --> 00:32:44,519
Maybe it's because I talked about

458
00:32:44,519 --> 00:32:45,799
about the ending of the novel,

459
00:32:48,400 --> 00:32:49,720
I was also hurt.

460
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:53,160
It seems that my prophecy

461
00:32:53,160 --> 00:32:54,720
of your old love

462
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:56,279
is coming true step by step.

463
00:32:57,880 --> 00:33:00,079
This is at most a recurrence of old wounds.

464
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:02,759
Isn't it scary?

465
00:33:02,759 --> 00:33:04,119
I tell you,

466
00:33:04,119 --> 00:33:05,640
you are now in the play for art.

467
00:33:05,640 --> 00:33:07,960
It's easy for you to get into the play but hard to get out of it.

468
00:33:08,319 --> 00:33:09,319
Did you forget
how long it took you

469
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:11,000
to forget him?

470
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:11,759
That was...

471
00:33:12,119 --> 00:33:13,680
That was after college, wasn't it?

472
00:33:13,680 --> 00:33:15,000
You still think of him from time to time.

473
00:33:15,680 --> 00:33:17,119
He is now

474
00:33:17,119 --> 00:33:19,160
entering your life again,

475
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:20,240
and leaving again.

476
00:33:20,799 --> 00:33:22,119
Back then, I didn't even get to see him

477
00:33:22,119 --> 00:33:23,039
one last time.

478
00:33:23,640 --> 00:33:24,200
That's why

479
00:33:24,200 --> 00:33:25,599
I've been dwelling on it for so long.

480
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:28,319
This time,

481
00:33:30,119 --> 00:33:31,400
I'll say a proper goodbye.

482
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:34,240
Then I'll be fine.

483
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,720
How to say a proper goodbye?

484
00:34:02,160 --> 00:34:03,160
No, no, no.

485
00:34:03,759 --> 00:34:04,920
Take a break.

486
00:34:06,039 --> 00:34:07,000
Did you

487
00:34:07,680 --> 00:34:08,760
get upset at his place?

488
00:34:08,760 --> 00:34:10,280
You're clearly taking it out on me.

489
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:11,239
Come on, bring it on.

490
00:34:11,599 --> 00:34:12,199
I'm done.

491
00:34:20,519 --> 00:34:21,000
Do you two

492
00:34:21,000 --> 00:34:22,079
have any misunderstandings?

493
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:25,559
Misunderstanding?

494
00:34:27,920 --> 00:34:28,480
When I was in the hospital,
she visited me

495
00:34:29,440 --> 00:34:30,320
and brought me porridge.

496
00:34:30,719 --> 00:34:31,639
Was that also a misunderstanding?

497
00:34:32,199 --> 00:34:33,480
Wasn't it you who sent her a WeChat message

498
00:34:33,480 --> 00:34:34,599
and asked her to come over?

499
00:34:35,039 --> 00:34:36,119
What about the fried rice cake?

500
00:34:37,559 --> 00:34:39,000
Didn't you say you were hungry?

501
00:34:40,239 --> 00:34:40,800
Yes.

502
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,480
Everything you just said

503
00:34:42,480 --> 00:34:43,719
was something I begged for.

504
00:34:44,159 --> 00:34:45,440
I was just being too hopeful.

505
00:34:47,920 --> 00:34:48,599
Yeah.

506
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:52,559
No, wait.

507
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:55,320
But,

508
00:34:56,719 --> 00:34:57,320
I can

509
00:34:57,320 --> 00:34:58,960
give you some advice now.

510
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:00,519
You always told me

511
00:35:00,519 --> 00:35:01,639
to stop being

512
00:35:01,639 --> 00:35:03,239
too hopeful.

513
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:05,840
I've learned a lot.

514
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:09,000
Listen,

515
00:35:09,960 --> 00:35:10,599
don't

516
00:35:11,480 --> 00:35:12,960
don't get too stuck in your ways.

517
00:35:13,559 --> 00:35:14,800
What's wrong with free candy?

518
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:17,159
Does it lose its sweetness?

519
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:20,119
If you get it, just enjoy it first.

520
00:35:20,400 --> 00:35:21,800
Finish it before you worry.

521
00:35:22,239 --> 00:35:22,719
Right?

522
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:24,639
It's not like

523
00:35:24,639 --> 00:35:26,239
you're being overly hopeful.

524
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:29,159
Just don't rush.

525
00:35:30,119 --> 00:35:31,199
Keep an eye on things.

526
00:35:31,519 --> 00:35:34,199
See if she still sends you candy

527
00:35:35,159 --> 00:35:36,559
when you're not asking for it.

528
00:35:42,440 --> 00:35:43,039
Right?

529
00:35:44,719 --> 00:35:45,360
Look,

530
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:47,000
speak of the devil, here's a message from her.

531
00:35:51,679 --> 00:35:53,559
[Dear lawyers, the trial is set for the day after tomorrow.]

532
00:35:53,559 --> 00:35:54,880
[Shall we meet at the court entrance?]

533
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:56,559
[If you're available tomorrow,]

534
00:35:56,559 --> 00:35:57,280
[come by the law firm.]

535
00:35:57,559 --> 00:35:58,719
[We'll go over some procedures]

536
00:35:58,760 --> 00:35:59,679
[with you.]

537
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:03,599
Not even a bit curious

538
00:36:03,599 --> 00:36:05,239
about what Ruan Yu said in the group?

539
00:36:08,599 --> 00:36:09,079
[Sure,]

540
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:10,440
but I have something in the morning.

541
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:11,360
Lawyer Liu,

542
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:12,519
when are you available this afternoon?

543
00:36:16,039 --> 00:36:16,800
I need to come early,

544
00:36:17,239 --> 00:36:18,840
I have an appointment later this afternoon.

545
00:36:22,559 --> 00:36:23,199
Xu,

546
00:36:24,079 --> 00:36:24,800
did you grow up

547
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:25,960
on willpower?

548
00:36:28,079 --> 00:36:29,840
You're clearly curious,

549
00:36:30,039 --> 00:36:31,440
but you won't even glance at your phone.

550
00:36:32,159 --> 00:36:32,679
I made it

551
00:36:32,679 --> 00:36:33,920
very clear from the start.

552
00:36:34,719 --> 00:36:35,679
I'm in charge of preparing the case,

553
00:36:36,159 --> 00:36:37,039
and you're in charge of the court.

554
00:36:37,599 --> 00:36:38,639
Now that my work

555
00:36:38,639 --> 00:36:39,440
is done,

556
00:36:40,079 --> 00:36:42,400
she's your client.

557
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:46,519
You've been using public resources for personal gain

558
00:36:46,519 --> 00:36:47,320
for so long,

559
00:36:47,320 --> 00:36:49,840
and now you're suddenly being so strict.

560
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:50,360
Right?

561
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:54,639
Fine, you're just being stubborn.

562
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:55,960
Don't trip yourself up.

563
00:36:59,239 --> 00:37:00,280
We have an appointment

564
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:01,039
I've scheduled a last

565
00:37:01,039 --> 00:37:02,199
pre-trial meeting with Ruan Yu.

566
00:37:02,559 --> 00:37:03,840
This is your last chance

567
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:04,920
to meet with her.

568
00:37:05,519 --> 00:37:06,840
Don't blame me for not warning you.

569
00:37:15,480 --> 00:37:16,199
Again?
Go on.

570
00:37:17,880 --> 00:37:19,199
Then go easy on me.

571
00:37:19,559 --> 00:37:20,719
Just a few more rounds.

572
00:37:24,599 --> 00:37:25,719
The live broadcast

573
00:37:25,719 --> 00:37:27,639
finally hit 50,000 viewers.

574
00:37:27,639 --> 00:37:28,800
Thanks for everyone's help.

575
00:37:33,239 --> 00:37:36,360
When are you coming back?

576
00:37:49,639 --> 00:37:50,280
Baby,

577
00:37:51,199 --> 00:37:52,480
why are your hands so cold?

578
00:37:53,519 --> 00:37:54,000
Are they?

579
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:56,159
Let me warm them up for you.

580
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:08,880
Warm them well.

581
00:38:32,800 --> 00:38:34,039
This wine smells good.

